Elevate your driving experience with this stunning 2025 BMW 4 Series 430i xDrive. Boasting a sleek Gray exterior and a sophisticated Mocha Vernasca leather interior, this certified pre-owned BMW is a true testament to German engineering and luxury.

Key features include:
M Sport Package
Shadowline Package
Premium Package
Harman/Kardon Surround Sound System
Front Ventilated Seats

Powered by a 2.0L 4-Cylinder TwinPower Turbo engine paired with an 8-Speed Automatic Sport transmission and BMW's renowned xDrive all-wheel-drive system, this 4 Series delivers an exhilarating yet efficient performance, achieving an impressive 27 MPG in the city and 34 MPG on the highway.

The M Sport Package elevates the driving dynamics with its Shadowline Exterior Trim, Black Mirror Caps, Aluminum Rhombicle Anthracite Trim, and M Steering Wheel, while the Shadowline Package further enhances the vehicle's sporty aesthetics with Full LED Headlights, Laserlight Taillights, and Extended Shadowline Trim.

For added comfort and convenience, the Premium Package includes Remote Engine Start, Power Tailgate, Comfort Access Keyless Entry, and the stunning BMW Curved Display with Head-Up Display. The Harman/Kardon Surround Sound System and Front Ventilated Seats provide a truly immersive and luxurious driving experience.

With only 10,921 miles on the odometer, this 2025 BMW 4 Series 430i xDrive is a remarkable opportunity to own a well-equipped, low-mileage, and meticulously maintained vehicle. Experience the unparalleled performance, technology, and style that only a BMW can deliver.

BMW Certified Pre-Owned Details:

Roadside Assistance
Transferable Warranty
Multipoint Point Inspection
Limited Warranty: 12 Month/Unlimited Mile
1 year/Unlimited miles beginning after new car warranty expires. 6-yrs Roadside Assistance. SiriusXM Satellite Radio 3-mos free. Every BMW Certified Plug-in Hybrid comes with an 8-Year/100,000-Mile Battery Guarantee. The Initial Battery Transfers to the New Owner.
Warranty Deductible: $0
Vehicle History

Don't miss your chance to own this exceptional 2025 BMW 4 Series 430i xDrive. Schedule a test drive today and discover the ultimate driving experience.

description:
Welcome to the perfect blend of performance and elegance with this Brilliant Blue Metallic 2022 Mercedes-Benz GLE 350 SUV. This vehicle is designed to make every journey feel special, whether you are running errands or heading out on a weekend getaway. Equipped with the 4MATIC all-wheel-drive system and a smooth 9-speed automatic transmission, this GLE 350 SUV offers a balanced and capable ride in various road conditions. The striking exterior is enhanced by the AMG Line Exterior and Night Package, featuring 20 inch AMG wheels with black accents that give this GLE 350 SUV a sporty and sophisticated edge.

Unmatched Comfort and Interior Luxury
Step inside the cabin of this GLE 350 SUV and you will be greeted by a world of premium materials and thoughtful design. You can truly relax with the Multicontour Front Seats that include a massage feature, perfect for staying comfortable during your commute. Both the driver and front passenger can enjoy ventilated and heated seats, ensuring you stay at the perfect temperature year-round. The Panorama Power Tilt and Sliding Sunroof opens up the cabin to plenty of natural light, while the genuine wood inserts on the dashboard and console provide a warm and high-quality feel throughout the interior of this GLE 350 SUV.

Advanced Technology at Your Fingertips
Staying connected and safe is effortless in this GLE 350 SUV. The Premium Package includes a beautiful 12.3 inch touchscreen display and a high-quality Burmester Surround Sound System for your favorite music. You will also have the Driver Assistance Package Plus, which acts like an extra set of eyes on the road. Features like Active Blind Spot Assist, Active Steering Assist, and the Surround View System help you navigate tight spots and busy highways with confidence. Plus, with Apple CarPlay and Android Auto, your favorite apps are always just a touch away in this GLE 350 SUV.

Ready for Your Next Adventure
This GLE 350 SUV is built to handle more than just the daily commute. It comes equipped with a trailer hitch and increased towing capacity, making it a versatile choice for those who enjoy outdoor activities. The Power Liftgate makes loading groceries or gear a breeze, and the foldable rear seats provide plenty of cargo space when you need it. Whether you are towing a small trailer or just packing up for a trip, this GLE 350 SUV is ready to support your lifestyle while maintaining the luxury you expect from a Mercedes-Benz.

Certified Pre-Owned Confidence
This one-owner GLE 350 SUV comes with a Clean CARFAX and the prestigious Mercedes-Benz Certified Pre-Owned status. This means the vehicle has undergone a rigorous 165+ point inspection by expert technicians. When you choose this certified GLE 350 SUV, you receive a 12 month unlimited mile limited warranty that begins after the new car warranty expires. You also get the added security of 24 hour roadside assistance and a $0 warranty deductible. It is a fantastic way to enjoy a premium vehicle with the long-term support and reliability you deserve.

*Burmester is a registered trademark of Burmester Audiosysteme GmbH, Berlin, Germany.

description:
Elevate Your Driving Experience with the 2023 Chevrolet Silverado 1500 RST

This remarkable 2023 Chevrolet Silverado 1500 RST is more than just a truck it's a command center on wheels, engineered to conquer any terrain and elevate your driving experience. With its powerful EcoTec3 5.3L V8 engine, 10-speed automatic transmission, and 4-wheel drive, this Silverado RST is ready to tackle any challenge you throw its way, whether it's navigating rugged off-road trails or effortlessly towing your boat or trailer.

All Star Edition Plus
Convenience Package II
High Capacity Suspension Package
Leather Package
Protection Package
Z71 Off-Road Package
Adaptive Cruise Control
Bose Premium Audio System
Dual-Zone Automatic Climate Control
Heated Steering Wheel
Wireless Charging
Heated Front Seats
Integrated Trailer Brake Controller

The Silverado RST's impressive capabilities are matched by its refined and sophisticated interior. Luxurious leather-appointed seating, a premium Bose audio system, and a 12.3-inch reconfigurable digital display create an environment that's as comfortable as it is capable. And with features like wireless charging, dual-zone climate control, and a heated steering wheel, you'll enjoy every mile of your journey.

But this Silverado RST is more than just a work truck it's a true all-rounder, designed to seamlessly transition from job site to family adventure. With the available Z71 Off-Road Package, you'll have the confidence to explore the great outdoors, while the Convenience Package II and Leather Package ensure you and your passengers travel in style and comfort.

Whether you're hauling heavy loads, towing your weekend toys, or simply enjoying the open road, the 2023 Chevrolet Silverado 1500 RST is the perfect companion. With its uncompromising performance, refined interior, and extensive suite of advanced features, this truck is the ultimate expression of capability and sophistication.

We invite you to experience the power and versatility of the 2023 Silverado 1500 RST for yourself. Schedule a test drive today and let us show you how this exceptional vehicle can elevate your driving experience.

description: JetStream Blue looks right on a C6, and this 2009 Corvette 3LT Z51 wears it like a tailored suit. It?s been garage kept and lightly used, with just 17,000 miles. The stance is clean and purposeful, finished off with forged chrome wheels that catch the light without shouting. Press the start button and the LS3 6.2L V8 comes to life with a deep, confident tone. With 436 hp and a 6-speed automatic, it pulls hard and stays smooth. The Z51 package adds the extra edge, and the dual-mode performance exhaust gives you two moods in one car, calm when you want it, bold when you don?t. Inside, the black leather cabin feels more grand tourer than bare-bones sports car. The 3LT trim brings the comfort you?ll notice on every drive, heated seats, power seats on both sides, driver memory, and dual-zone climate control. The heads-up display keeps your eyes forward, and the Bose audio, XM, Bluetooth, CD, and factory navigation keep the ride easy to live with. Add keyless entry, cruise control, power windows and locks, universal home remote, fog lights, and OnStar, and it?s ready for both date nights and backroad runs. If you want a garage kept Corvette that looks sharp, sounds right, and feels special every time you drive it, this one fits. Elevate Your Driving Experience with this Exceptional 2019 BMW X3 M40i

Discover the ultimate blend of performance, luxury, and cutting-edge technology in this stunning 2019 BMW X3 M40i. With its powerful I6 engine, 8-speed automatic transmission, and intelligent all-wheel-drive system, this dynamic SUV delivers an exhilarating driving experience that will leave you craving the open road.

Backed by our Lifetime Powertrain Protection
Original MSRP $67,970
Driving Assistance Package
Driving Assistance Plus Package
Executive Package
Wireless Charging

Indulge in the premium features that set this BMW X3 M40i apart, including the remarkable harman/kardon Surround Sound System, power moonroof, and power liftgate. Stay connected and secure with the Active Blind Spot Detection, Lane Departure Warning System, and Rear-View Camera, while the Active Driving Assistant and Extended Collision Mitigation provide added peace of mind.

Elevate your driving experience with the Dynamic Digital Instrument Cluster, Enhanced USB & Bluetooth, and Gesture Control. Enjoy the comfort of heated front seats and the Vernasca Leather Upholstery, while the Surround View with 3D View and WiFi Hotspot ensure you're always connected and in command.

This exceptional BMW X3 M40i also boasts a wealth of additional features, including a Navigation System, 12-speaker Hi-Fi Sound System, and Automatic Climate Control. The Adaptive M Suspension and Four-Wheel Independent Suspension deliver a smooth and responsive ride, while the powerful 4-Wheel Disc Brakes and Electronic Stability Control provide confident control.

Whether you're seeking a thrilling performance SUV or a refined and sophisticated daily driver, this 2019 BMW X3 M40i is the perfect choice. With its exceptional features, uncompromising quality, and unparalleled driving dynamics, this vehicle is sure to exceed your expectations.

Cruise control only managed speed, but not distance or safety. Now, with Adaptive cruise control with traffic stop-go, simply set your desired speed and let sensor technology maintain a safe distance between you and the vehicle ahead. It's stop/go feature automatically brings the vehicle to a stop if traffic stops and resumes distance pacing cruise when traffic starts to move again. Adaptive cruise control with traffic stop-go; your ultimate co-pilot. Adaptive cruise control with traffic stop-go. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful. Adaptive cruise control with traffic stop-go; your ultimate co-pilot.Safety and Security Hands-on cruise control. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful. Cruise control only managed speed, but not distance or safety. Now, with hands-on cruise control, simply set your desired speed and let sensor technology maintain a safe distance between you and surrounding vehicles. It slows you down; speeds you up and even keeps you in your own lane. Meet your ultimate co-pilot with hands-on cruise control. Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. description:
Get ready to turn heads in this stunning designo Cardinal Red Metallic 2020 Mercedes-Benz GLC 300 SUV! This isn't just an SUV, its a statement of sophistication and performance, beautifully combining the utility you need with the luxury you deserve. Beneath its eye catching exterior, you'll find a lively I4 engine paired with a smooth 9-Speed Automatic transmission, offering impressive fuel economy of 22/29 City/Highway MPG while providing a dynamic Rear Wheel Drive experience. It's ready for any adventure you plan, from your daily commute to weekend escapes.

Certified Confidence and Premium Comfort
Drive with ultimate peace of mind knowing this GLC 300 SUV is Mercedes-Benz Certified Pre-Owned. That means it's passed a rigorous 165+ Point Inspection and comes with an exceptional warranty, including a Limited Warranty for 12 months with unlimited miles after the new car warranty expires, a $0 Warranty Deductible, and invaluable features like Roadside Assistance and a Transferable Warranty. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of comfort and technology. You'll love the Heated Front Bucket Seats, the luxurious feel of the MB-Tex Upholstery, and the convenience of the Power Driver Seat & Steering Column with Memory. Setting the mood is easy with the vibrant 64-Color Ambient Lighting that transforms the interior at night.

Technology That Connects and Delights
This Mercedes-Benz GLC 300 SUV is loaded with cutting edge tech designed to make every drive easier and more enjoyable. The centerpiece is the impressive 10.25 Center Touchscreen Display which houses the MBUX Multimedia System. You've got seamless integration with Apple CarPlay/Android Auto and the futuristic MBUX Voice Control system, making navigation and entertainment a breeze. Parking is simple thanks to the Exterior Parking Camera Rear, and the KEYLESS GO feature means you'll never have to fumble for your keys. Other thoughtful touches include Illuminated Door Sills, LED Logo Projectors, and the built-in convenience of SiriusXM Satellite Radio.

Open Air Luxury with Panoramic Views
Experience the open road in a whole new light with the expansive Panorama Sunroof. Whether it's letting in the bright sunshine or offering a view of the night sky, it adds an extra dimension of luxury to the drive. The Premium Package further enhances the experience with features like the Power Liftgate, KEYLESS GO, and more. The attention to detail is evident everywhere, from the Genuine wood dashboard insert to the sophisticated look of the 18 Split 5-Spoke Wheels. Practicality hasn't been forgotten, either, with features like the Fully automatic headlights, rain sensing wipers, and front dual zone A/C.

This Certified Pre-Owned 2020 Mercedes-Benz GLC 300 SUV delivers an unparalleled blend of style, advanced features, and certified reliability. It's truly a magnificent vehicle that's ready to elevate your daily driving experience. Don't miss the opportunity to make this spectacular designo Cardinal Red Metallic luxury SUV yours!

*Vehicle Details*
Ready for weekend trails and weekday commutes, this 2024 Ford Bronco Sport Big Bend is a standout blend of capability and comfort with only 6,115 miles. Rugged yet refined, the Big Bend trim pairs a peppy 3-cylinder 1.5L engine with 4WD confidence for tackling dirt roads, snowy lanes, or city streets with equal ease. The sporty exterior cues and functional roof rails hint at adventure, while the thoughtfully appointed interior keeps passengers comfortable and connected. Safety and convenience are front and center: a Back-Up Camera makes parking and hitching a breeze, Cross-Traffic Alert adds peace of mind in busy lots, and Hands-Free Bluetooth keeps your focus on the road while streaming calls and music. This Ford Bronco Sport comes with a CARFAX Clean Report and is a CARFAX 1-Owner vehicle, offering added reassurance about its history and care. Well-equipped, dependable, and hassle-free, this Ford Bronco Sport Big Bend is ready to join your active lifestyle. Whether you?re loading gear for a weekend escape or navigating daily errands, it offers the versatility and reliability you want. Low miles, proven service history, and thoughtful features make this a smart, exciting choice for your next adventure.

This 2024 Ford Bronco Sport keeps you comfortable with Auto Climate. This mid-size suv's Cross-Traffic Alert: Safeguarding you from unexpected traffic when reversing. This mid-size suv has four wheel drive capabilities. This Ford Bronco Sport has a 3 Cyl, 1.5L high output engine. Maintaining a stable interior temperature in it is easy with the climate control system. This mid-size suv has an automatic transmission. This mid-size suv features cruise control for long trips.

description:
2025 Hyundai Elantra SEL Convenience Smart, Comfortable & Tech-Rich Compact Sedan

The 2025 Hyundai Elantra SEL Convenience elevates the popular Elantra lineup with enhanced comfort, modern technology, and practical features that make daily driving easier and more enjoyable. Positioned as a well-equipped mid-tier trim, the SEL Convenience delivers an excellent balance of style, efficiency, and value.

Efficient Performance

Engine: Smooth and efficient 2.0-liter 4-cylinder

Power: 147 hp with responsive performance for city and highway driving

Transmission: Smartstream® Intelligent Variable Transmission (IVT)

Fuel Economy: Approximately 30 mpg city / 39 mpg highway with 34 mpg combined great for everyday commuting and longer trips.

This powertrain delivers a refined and economical ride that s ideal for daily errands, commuting, and weekend adventures.

Comfort & Convenience

Inside the SEL Convenience, you ll appreciate thoughtful upgrades that enhance the driving experience:

Heated front seats perfect for chilly mornings

Power sunroof for open-air enjoyment

Supportive seating with plenty of room for up to five passengers

60/40 split-folding rear seatback for added cargo flexibility

These features help make every drive more comfortable and adaptable to your lifestyle.

Advanced Technology & Connectivity

Stay connected and entertained with an engaging tech suite:

10.25 touchscreen navigation intuitive and easy to use

10.25 digital instrument cluster modern and informative

Apple CarPlay® and Android Auto integration

Bluetooth® hands-free phone system and wireless device charging

Second-row USB charging ports and SiriusXM® satellite radio

This technology package keeps you connected, entertained, and informed on every drive.

Safety & Driving Confidence

The SEL Convenience includes a suite of standard safety features designed to help protect you and your passengers:

Forward Collision-Avoidance Assist with pedestrian, cyclist, and junction-turning detection

Blind-Spot Collision Warning

Lane Keeping Assist and Lane Following Assist

Rear Cross-Traffic Collision-Avoidance Assist

Driver Attention Warning and High Beam Assist

Rear View Monitor for easier backing and parking

These systems work together to enhance on-road confidence and safety.

Exterior & Practical Details

Sleek, modern Elantra styling with 17 alloy wheels

LED lighting accents

Hands-free smart trunk with auto open

Clean, aerodynamic profile that stands out in the compact sedan segment

In summary:
The 2025 Hyundai Elantra SEL Convenience delivers a well-rounded blend of comfort, technology, and efficiency ideal for buyers who want a compact sedan that s smartly equipped without reaching luxury pricing. It s a great choice for commuters, small families, or anyone who values modern features, comfort on the road, and everyday usability.

CARFAX One-Owner. Clean CARFAX.

Please call 901-410-2894 for details!

description:
This Black 2019 Mercedes-Benz C-Class C 300 Sedan is the perfect introduction to the world of luxury driving. It comes with a Clean Carfax and has undergone a thorough Multi-Point Inspection to ensure it is ready for the road. Powered by a responsive 2.0L turbocharged engine, this Mercedes-Benz C-Class C 300 Sedan offers a sporty yet fuel-efficient experience that makes it a joy to drive through city streets or out on the open highway.

The exterior of this Mercedes-Benz C-Class C 300 Sedan is highlighted by elegant 18 inch Multispoke wheels with black accents, giving it a modern and sophisticated look. You can enjoy the fresh air with the built-in Power Moonroof, and the auto-dimming mirrors help keep your vision clear when driving at night. With the KEYLESS GO system, you can unlock and start your car without ever having to take your keys out of your pocket or bag.

Inside the cabin, you will find a refined space filled with genuine wood inserts on the console, dashboard, and door panels. The Heated Front Seats and dual zone automatic temperature control ensure that you and your passenger stay perfectly comfortable regardless of the weather outside. This Mercedes-Benz C-Class C 300 Sedan also features power front seats with memory settings, so your favorite driving position is saved and ready for you every time you get behind the wheel.

Staying connected is simple thanks to the Premium Package, which includes Apple CarPlay and Android Auto integration. You can easily access your maps, messages, and music on the go, while SiriusXM Satellite Radio provides a wide variety of entertainment. This Mercedes-Benz C-Class C 300 Sedan even includes a HANDS-FREE Comfort Package with an Electronic Trunk Closer, allowing you to open the trunk with a simple kick motion under the rear bumper when your hands are full.

Safety is a top priority in this Mercedes-Benz C-Class C 300 Sedan, which is equipped with Blind Spot Assist to help you change lanes with confidence. The Exterior Parking Camera Rear makes backing up safer and easier, while the rain-sensing wipers automatically adjust to keep your windshield clear. Whether you are looking for a stylish daily driver or a comfortable long-distance cruiser, this sedan offers the quality and prestige you expect from Mercedes-Benz.

2001 Chevy Silverado 2500HD Duramax Diesel
Strong Reliable Road-Ready

Selling my 2001 Chevy Silverado 2500HD LS with the 6.6L

Duramax LB7 and Allison automatic.

This adult owned, no emissions truck is tough, dependable, and ready to work or travel anywhere. It has never once let me down. I have no hesitation towing my boat or jetskis across the state. No blow by, no smoke and injector rates are good. Only selling because our girls car seats don't fit and we are tired of taking two cars camping, boating etc...

Quick Facts:
226K miles on body
Only ~100K miles on the motor
4x4 LS trim
Clean title in hand
Many upgraded parts
Hot heat
Power windows & locks

Tow package Good overall condition for its age. Aftermarket parts include air intake inlet horn, PPE 1" down pipe, PPE exhaust manifolds, powermaster starter, XDP X-TRA transmission cooler.

Note: Check Engine Light is on, but it doesn't affect drivability. Runs smooth and strong I'd drive it across the country without hesitation. AC needs to be recharged.

Asking: $11,500 OBO (reasonable offers welcome)
Located in [Bonney Lake, WA]

Message me if you're serious this Duramax is ready to roll!

This 2018 Subaru Outback 2.5i Premium is a versatile and well-equipped SUV that's ready to take on your next adventure. With its impressive all-wheel-drive capability, advanced safety features, and premium amenities, this Outback is the perfect blend of capability and comfort.

Key features of this Outback include:
EyeSight & BSD & RCTA & Power Rear Gate & HBA
AM/FM radio: SiriusXM, CD player, Subaru STARLINK 8.0 Multimedia Plus System
Front dual zone A/C, Power driver seat, Power Rear Gate with Automatic Close & Height Memory
Adaptive Cruise Control, Heated door mirrors, High Beam Assist (HBA)
Apple CarPlay/Android Auto, Blind Spot Detection (BSD), Lane Departure Warning & Sway Warning, Rear Cross Traffic Alert (RCTA)

This Outback's 2.5L 4-cylinder DOHC engine and Lineartronic CVT transmission deliver an exceptional balance of power and efficiency, with an EPA-estimated 25 city/32 highway MPG. The all-wheel-drive system provides confident handling and traction, whether you're navigating winding roads or tackling inclement weather.

The interior of this Outback is both stylish and functional, with premium cloth upholstery, heated front seats, a power driver's seat, and a versatile 60/40 split-folding rear seat. The Subaru STARLINK infotainment system keeps you connected and entertained, with features like Apple CarPlay, Android Auto, and SiriusXM satellite radio.

Safety is also a top priority, with Subaru's renowned EyeSight driver assist technology, which includes adaptive cruise control, pre-collision braking, lane departure and sway warning, and more. Additionally, the Outback boasts a suite of advanced safety features, including blind spot detection, rear cross-traffic alert, and high beam assist.

Whether you're looking for a capable family SUV, a versatile adventure vehicle, or a premium daily driver, this 2018 Subaru Outback 2.5i Premium is an exceptional choice. Visit our showroom today to experience its impressive capabilities and premium features for yourself.
